<style>
.faq { padding:80px 0; }
.faq-title { text-align:center;font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:48px; }
.faq-list { max-width:720px;margin:0 auto; }
.faq-item { border-bottom:1px solid var(--brand-border);padding:20px 0; }
.faq-q { font-size:16px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;margin-bottom:4px; }
.faq-a { font-size:14px;color:var(--brand-gray);line-height:1.6; }
</style>
<section class="faq container">
  <h2 class="faq-title">FAQ</h2>
  <div class="faq-list">
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How do I know which size to order?</div><div class="faq-a">Measure your knee 10cm above the kneecap. S (30-34cm), M (34-38cm), L (38-42cm). When in doubt, size down for a secure compression fit.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Can I wear it on both knees?</div><div class="faq-a">Yes — each sleeve is sold individually. Many hikers buy the 2-pack for both knees and save 20%.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Does it work for trail running?</div><div class="faq-a">Absolutely. The anti-slip grip keeps it firmly in place even during high-impact technical descents.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How long does delivery take?</div><div class="faq-a">7-11 working days to Europe and North America. Free tracked shipping on all orders.</div></div>
  </div>
</section>
